<text><body>
<lb n="0610c03"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0610c04"/>
<lb n="0610c05"/><head type="no">No. 1511</head>
<lb n="0610c06"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0610001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本</note>修習般若波羅蜜菩薩觀行念誦
<lb n="0610c07"/>儀軌<note n="0610002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【甲】</note><app n="0610002"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0610c08"/>
<lb n="0610c09"/><byline type="Translator">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0610c10"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑑
<lb n="0610c11"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門
<lb n="0610c12"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0610c13"/><div1 type="jing"><lg><l>歸命般若母</l><l>清淨妙法身</l>
<lb n="0610c14"/><l>我今依瑜伽</l><l>演說觀行法</l>
<lb n="0610c15"/><l>運心遍法界</l><l>一切佛剎海</l>
<lb n="0610c16"/><l>想身周圍遶</l><l>由是得解脫</l>
<lb n="0610c17"/><l>想身遶諸佛</l><l>一一諸佛前</l>
<lb n="0610c18"/><l>菩薩眾圍遶</l><l>持妙供養具</l>
<lb n="0610c19"/><l>三世諸如來</l><l>及大菩薩眾</l>
<lb n="0610c20"/><l>緣覺與聲聞</l><l>一切正法藏</l>
<lb n="0610c21"/><l>皆悉盡無餘</l><l>遍想於己身</l>
<lb n="0610c22"/><l>一切<note n="0610003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乃＝及【甲】，彼&M062403;【甲】</note><note n="0610003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃＝及【甲】，＝彼&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0610003"><lem>乃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">及</rdg><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">彼</rdg></app>眾前</l><l>分明如對目</l>
<lb n="0610c23"/><l>皆從淨心生</l><l>廣多供養具</l>
<lb n="0610c24"/><l>作無量供養</l><l>無間<note n="0610004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&M010527;＝應【甲】</note><app n="0610004"><lem>&M010527;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">應</rdg></app>作禮</l>
<lb n="0610c25"/><l>宮殿妙拂蓋</l><l>無數眾樓閣</l>
<lb n="0610c26"/><l>花鬘末塗香</l><l>種種寶莊嚴</l>
<lb n="0610c27"/><l>彼諸供養儀</l><l>遍滿虛空界</l>
<lb n="0610c28"/><l>殷勤心加持</l><l>奉獻諸如來</l>
<lb n="0610c29"/><l>如空剎土爾</l><l>如剎佛亦然</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1151.0611a" n="0611a"/>
<lb n="0611a01"/><note n="0611001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（如佛…量）十五字＝（佛法既無窮供養悉周遍一心&M010527;供養）十五字&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0611001" word-count="15"><lem><l>如佛法亦然</l><l>如法供養然</l>
<lb n="0611a02"/><l>一切皆無量</l></lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">佛法既無窮供養悉周遍一心&M010527;供養</rdg></app><l>十方無邊剎</l>
<lb n="0611a03"/><l>知已作是言</l><l><note n="0611002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">敬禮諸如來＝普禮佛法海&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0611002"><lem>敬禮諸如來</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">普禮佛法海</rdg></app></l></lg>
<lb n="0611a04"/><p>遍禮一切如來真言曰</p>
<lb n="0611a05"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;怛他<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00617;多<note place="inline">一</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>那滿<note n="0611003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曩＝娜&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0611003"><lem>曩</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">娜</rdg></app><note place="inline">上引</note>喃迦
<lb n="0611a06"/>嚕<note place="inline">引</note>弭<note place="inline">二</note></p>
<lb n="0611a07"/><lg><l>種種勝無量</l><l>大乘經所說</l>
<lb n="0611a08"/><l>陀羅尼佛心</l><l>殷勤應稱誦</l>
<lb n="0611a09"/><l>當生淨信心</l><l>專注於一境</l>
<lb n="0611a10"/><l>為諸有情類</l><l>觀察勝菩提</l>
<lb n="0611a11"/><l>即當作偏袒</l><l>右膝而著地</l>
<lb n="0611a12"/><l>誠心合掌住</l><l>應作如是言</l>
<lb n="0611a13"/><l>自作教他作</l><l>或自他隨喜</l>
<lb n="0611a14"/><l>由身口意罪</l><l>願諸佛哀愍</l>
<lb n="0611a15"/><l>今生一億罪</l><l>乃至無始世</l>
<lb n="0611a16"/><l>及當坐菩提</l><l>不復更違犯</l>
<lb n="0611a17"/><l>如是勝懺悔</l><l>真實觀察故</l>
<lb n="0611a18"/><l>以佛願智火</l><l>焚盡無有餘</l>
<lb n="0611a19"/><l>能取及所取</l><l>一切皆唯心</l>
<lb n="0611a20"/><l>佛剎等供養</l><l>能取所取意</l>
<lb n="0611a21"/><l>菩薩住等引</l><l>見心如影像</l>
<lb n="0611a22"/><l>能取想分別</l><l>安住於空性</l>
<lb n="0611a23"/><l><note n="0611004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝一&M062485;【甲】</note><sic n="0611004" corr="一" resp="【甲】">二</sic>性無性相</l><l>是名為空相</l>
<lb n="0611a24"/><l>無性非無性</l><l>不離於一性</l>
<lb n="0611a25"/><l>能所及供養</l><l>三種離分別</l>
<lb n="0611a26"/><l>由無分別故</l><l>此供養為勝</l>
<lb n="0611a27"/><l>如是勝供養</l><l>及以旋遶法</l>
<lb n="0611a28"/><l>一切重罪咎</l><l><note n="0611005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">除滅皆＝滅盡令&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0611005"><lem>除滅皆</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">滅盡令</rdg></app>無餘</l>
<lb n="0611a29"/><l>貪性知無貪</l><l>即入貪性空</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1151.0611b" n="0611b"/>
<lb n="0611b01"/><l>瞋性知無瞋</l><l>即入瞋性空</l>
<lb n="0611b02"/><l>癡性知無癡</l><l>即入癡性空</l>
<lb n="0611b03"/><l>如是於諸惑</l><l>觀察實相理</l>
<lb n="0611b04"/><l>有此智慧者</l><l>由空無分別</l>
<lb n="0611b05"/><l>如蓮華處水</l><l>不著諸罪咎</l></lg>
<lb n="0611b06"/><p>修行者作如是觀照。淨身心已即結三昧耶
<lb n="0611b07"/>印</p>
<lb n="0611b08"/><lg><l>二羽相交合</l><l>當安於心上</l>
<lb n="0611b09"/><l>遍觀虛空佛</l><l>誦真言三遍</l></lg>
<lb n="0611b10"/><p><note n="0611006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔真言曰〕&M062403;－【甲】＊</note><app n="0611006"><lem>真言曰</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0611b11"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0611007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔唵〕&M062403;－【甲】＊</note><app n="0611007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00085;日<note n="0611008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03298;一＝囉二【甲】</note><note n="0611008" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>&CB03298;一＝囉二【甲】</note>&CB03298;<note place="inline">一合引</note>惹禮</p>
<lb n="0611b12"/><p>次結金剛縛。十度外相叉。密縛成印相。金剛
<lb n="0611b13"/>縛真言。<app type="＊" source="0611006"><lem>真言曰</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0611b14"/><p type="dharani">&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱</p>
<lb n="0611b15"/><lg><l>如前金剛縛</l><l>掣擊於心上</l>
<lb n="0611b16"/><l>能滅諸結使</l><l>開顯解脫宮</l></lg>
<lb n="0611b17"/><p><note n="0611009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（即當…曰）八字＝（字想安於二乳即誦開心真言每誦掣開心戶）十八字&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0611009" word-count="8"><lem>即當誦開心真言曰</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">字想安於二乳即誦開心真言每誦掣開心戶</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0611b18"/><p type="dharani">&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吒<note place="inline">吒半音呼</note></p>
<lb n="0611b19"/><lg><l>次結發智印</l><l>如前金剛縛</l>
<lb n="0611b20"/><l>定慧入於掌</l><l>召入圓寂智</l>
<lb n="0611b21"/><l><note n="0611010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">召入於＝即誦召入&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0611010"><lem>召入於</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">即誦召入</rdg></app>種智</l></lg>
<lb n="0611b22"/><p>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0611b23"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0611007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>吠舍惡</p>
<lb n="0611b24"/><lg><l>次結金剛拳</l><l>進力<note n="0611011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跓＝拄【甲】</note><app n="0611011"><lem>跓</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">拄</rdg></app>禪<note n="0611012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＋（以附拄心門）&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0611012"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">智以附拄心門</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0611b25"/><l>金剛身語意</l><l>密合不傾動</l></lg>
<lb n="0611b26"/><p><note n="0611013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（即）&M062403;＋誦【甲】＊</note><app n="0611013"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">即誦</rdg></app>金剛拳真言曰</p>
<lb n="0611b27"/><p type="dharani">&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>畝瑟置<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0611014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00805;＝&CB00680;&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0611014"><lem>&CB00805;</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">&CB00680;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0611b28"/><lg><l>即結三昧耶</l><l>自成普賢故</l>
<lb n="0611b29"/><l><note n="0611015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">結已＝縛以&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0611015"><lem>結已</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">縛以</rdg></app>&CB00594;忍願</l><l>身處於月輪</l></lg>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1151.0611c" n="0611c"/>
<lb n="0611c01"/><p>即誦三昧耶真言曰</p>
<lb n="0611c02"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0611007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>三麼野薩怛&CB00680;<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0611c03"/><lg><l>次結大真誓</l><l>忍願<note n="0611016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝交&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0611016"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">交</rdg></app>入縛</l>
<lb n="0611c04"/><l>檀慧定智&CB00594;</l><l>二度三觸心</l>
<lb n="0611c05"/><l>藏識厭離種</l><l>能除悲增長</l></lg>
<lb n="0611c06"/><p><note n="0611017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復當誦真言曰〕－【甲】</note><app n="0611017"><lem>復當誦真言曰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0611c07"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0611007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>三麼野護素囉多薩怛&CB00680;<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0611c08"/><lg><l>次應作辟除</l><l>結金剛藥叉</l>
<lb n="0611c09"/><l>二羽金剛拳</l><l>檀慧進力屈</l>
<lb n="0611c10"/><l>置於口兩頰</l><l>想身同彼尊</l>
<lb n="0611c11"/><l>厲聲誦真言</l><l>左右而顧視</l></lg>
<lb n="0611c12"/><p><note n="0611018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（即誦）&M062403;＋金【甲】＊</note><app n="0611018"><lem>金</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">即誦金</rdg></app>剛藥叉真言曰</p>
<lb n="0611c13"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0611007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>藥乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00292;</p>
<lb n="0611c14"/><lg><l>所有諸障者</l><l>悉皆四馳散</l>
<lb n="0611c15"/><l>二目想麼吒</l><l>轉如日月輪</l>
<lb n="0611c16"/><l>止觀金剛拳</l><l>各安於二&CB03437;</l>
<lb n="0611c17"/><l>隨日作旋視</l><l>以成十方界</l></lg>
<lb n="0611c18"/><p><app type="＊" source="0611013"><lem>誦</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">即誦</rdg></app>金剛眼真言曰</p>
<lb n="0611c19"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>瑟知<note place="inline">二合</note>麼<note n="0611019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吒＋（半音呼）細註&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0611019"><lem>吒</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">吒<note place="inline">半音呼</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0611c20"/><lg><l>當入三摩地</l><l>縛印相如前</l>
<lb n="0611c21"/><l>仰安結跏上</l><l>端身須正直</l>
<lb n="0611c22"/><l>閉目入正定</l><l>遍觀虛空佛</l>
<lb n="0611c23"/><l>盡滿如胡麻</l><l>彼一切如來</l>
<lb n="0611c24"/><l>憶昔誓願故</l><l>異口同音聲</l>
