<lb n="0612a19"/><l>如鬘頂後繫</l><l>垂下勢如帶</l></lg>
<lb n="0612a20"/><p><note n="0612005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（即誦）&M062403;＋一【甲】</note><app n="0612005"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">即誦一</rdg></app>切如來寶冠真言曰</p>
